Seller will contribute $2500 toward buyer closing costs and pay $650 toward Residential Service Contract. *Seller Motivated!
Home has undergone significant remodeling, featuring all-new Anderson Windows, flooring, paint, baseboards, lighting fixtures, countertops and a privacy fence! There is also an adorable chicken coop!
This home is within a mile+ to schools and a Starbucks, making your daily routines a breeze. 
With all the hard work already done, you won't have to worry about updating a single aspect of this home. It's move-in ready and waiting to welcome you with open arms. If you dream of living close to town amenities without the stress of renovating, then look no further. This property is your ideal choice.
Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this fabulous house your new home. Call/Text *1 hour notice* Pets on premises
Items that don't convey with the house: two refrigerators, washer/dryer, curtains, & tv wall mounts
